<p>It started with generating some samples using the good old <a href="http://www.drpetter.se/project_sfxr.html">SXFR</a>. It‚Äôs a tiny sythesizer for generating cute oldschool chiptune/game sound effects. Sadly it doesn‚Äôt exist as <a href="https://flathub.org">an app</a>, which is a shame.</p>

